Well, I did say 11 o'clock sharp and it's now five past.
嗯，我确实说了11点整，现在已经过了五分钟。

119
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:27,880
So...
所以……

120
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,040
Hi, everyone.
大家好。

121
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,640
I'm so sorry I'm late.
非常抱歉我迟到了。

122
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:34,960
It's raining cats and dogs outside and I had to wait ages for a taxi.
外面下着倾盆大雨，我等出租车等了很久。

123
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:36,240
Okay, James.
好的，詹姆斯。

124
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,800
Take a seat quickly, please.
请快点坐下。

125
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,800
Right.
好的。

126
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:41,040
The subject of the meeting is the importance...
会议的主题是重要性……

127
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,040
Hi, guys.
嗨，大家好。

128
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,200
Please excuse me.
请原谅我。

129
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:45,280
I was held up in traffic.
我被交通堵住了。

130
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:46,520
Right.
好的。

131
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:48,800
As I was saying, the subject of the meeting is...
正如我刚才说的，会议的主题是……

132
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,800
Hi, Maggie.
嗨，玛吉。

133
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,080
I'm terribly sorry.
我非常抱歉。

134
