我们经常听到“hang on a sec”或“wait a sec”。

160
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:55,760
Wait a sec.
等一下。

161
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:56,760
Uh-huh.
嗯哼。

162
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,760
Okay, very good.
好的，非常好。

163
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:59,120
So, it's very casual.
所以，这非常随意。

164
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:03,240
